{"id": 2021, "genre": 1001, "title": "对于哪些套餐服务，你希望能够推出“轻量版”？", "description": "至少，捆绑销售别做得太明显了。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3143, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171120135118WAZsQIaVUvPzHG76.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-21T03:00:27Z", "options": [{"id": 250112, "content": "校园的套餐，加了一堆用不到的咪咕定向流量和不好用的cmcc，即使关掉也不会优惠，", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154007}, {"id": 250113, "content": "校园卡的话费套餐，通话时间基本没有消耗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078363}, {"id": 250121, "content": "为生活，做减法；为思想，做加法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189619}, {"id": 251657, "content": "我只要流量和电话多一点，靓号真的不需要", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204323}, {"id": 250122, "content": "迅雷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822188}, {"id": 250123, "content": "买手机膜送手机支架，?每回都有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031566}, {"id": 250124, "content": "支付宝只要支付，微信只要信息，迅雷只要下载，杀毒软件只要杀毒", "image": null, "praise_count": 306, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103595}, {"id": 250125, "content": "淘宝评价礼品2元流量劵", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187678}, {"id": 250126, "content": "杀毒不要全家桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535986}, {"id": 250127, "content": "卤味烧烤等食物能轻口一些", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 52862}, {"id": 250129, "content": "支付宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093236}, {"id": 250130, "content": "餐包？搞什么鬼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154871}, {"id": 250643, "content": "淘宝卖家不要再送小镜子和防尘塞了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138453}, {"id": 252436, "content": "运营商的各种套餐的说明很乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202682}, {"id": 250133, "content": "蚊香液这种，买一次带加热器的套装就足够了，但是单独的蚊香液偏偏比套装贵，于是多了一堆没用的加热器。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195734}, {"id": 249878, "content": "视频网站只需要去广告，不需要乱七八糟的观影券、自制节目", "image": null, "praise_count": 309, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 250134, "content": "我居然看成了套套服务。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184454}, {"id": 249879, "content": "移动运营商的通话和流量总有一个用不完，找不到完全契合自己需要的版本", "image": null, "praise_count": 579, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 250135, "content": "大家说的太多了，\n好像也太对了，\n看不完了。\n能不能轻量精简?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982048}, {"id": 249880, "content": "旅游网站的机酒套餐还要加保险和车辆接送，根本用不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 250136, "content": "视频网站", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189179}, {"id": 249881, "content": "搭售的彩妆配好的颜色总是有一两个不喜欢的，如果能减掉或换掉一定会买", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 250138, "content": "影院的小食套餐，不要那么多爆米花能不能便宜点", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 250395, "content": "视频网站可不可以不要放那么多广告？！比如走优酷，前几年就十多秒，现在要1分半钟，而且中间要加两次广告！没有底线的延长广告！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619287}, {"id": 250142, "content": "快餐一定要可乐好不好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280641}, {"id": 250144, "content": "迅雷这种能不能推出“日会员”，今天用的多我买两毛钱会员就行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173486}, {"id": 250145, "content": "理发", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 19741}, {"id": 250146, "content": "接机套餐，根本不用", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 19741}, {"id": 250147, "content": "题图竟然看饿了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923935}, {"id": 250148, "content": "电脑下载软件可不可以不要捆绑安装(´･_･`)", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292692}, {"id": 250154, "content": "餐厅的套餐可不可以不要给一堆沙拉", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187198}, {"id": 250157, "content": "买二送一 三个起卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164162}, {"id": 251181, "content": "我真的只想买两根葱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195942}, {"id": 250158, "content": "还有 第二个半价 你却一个人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164162}, {"id": 250161, "content": "必胜客\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 250162, "content": "我可能是个异类，我希望手机只用来打电话发信息，玩游戏用游戏机，看书用阅读器，听歌就用播放器，我需要单一功能做到最好的设备，不需要多功能", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68429}, {"id": 345907, "content": "淘宝的什么乱七八糟各种各样五花八门的活动！！各种优惠券入口！！！各种隐形优惠券等等！！头都大了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570803}, {"id": 258355, "content": "食物有半份的就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232094}, {"id": 250164, "content": "网易云不要视频。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 251199, "content": "飞机✈️不要收机建燃油", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196115}, {"id": 250177, "content": "Dayone，只需要同步功能+Mac和iOS的软件使用，88元一年可以接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752865}, {"id": 250178, "content": "卖手机送贴膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189872}, {"id": 250181, "content": "饿了么会员，不想要减钱券，想要免送费", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179056}, {"id": 252230, "content": "聘：煎直人